sql_json.natural_language: List unread emails from the past month.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE isUnread = true AND sentAt >= TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 1 MONTH) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;

sdk_json.from_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE isUnread = true AND sentAt >= TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 1 MONTH) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
